    Template selector which attempts to select a template from a given ITemplates object based on the value of the message field associated with a particular field tag number - the selector tag number.

    It will match the value of that field against templates by searching for a template that has a field with an id matching the selector tag number and a constant operator with a value equal to the message field's value.

    The default selecting field number is 35 - which matches the tag number of the MsgType field in the FIX protocol.
